<p>In jqgrid initially I am loading blank rows (10)as per client requirement, so initially no json data is loaded.</p>  <p>I have search textbox and button for searching. Before searching I have load json now my problem is when I am searching data first time, it will load all data (filter is not applied). I have tried search <code>search:true</code> but not working.</p>  <p>So filter is working only when data is in grid, but I donâ€™t want like that data should filter from json itself. Below is the sample code which I am using search is implement for 1st column. </p>  <p>I have upload files for referance: <a href="http://123.63.211.244:90/vishal/filter/poc.html" rel="nofollow">http://123.63.211.244:90/vishal/filter/poc.html</a></p>  <pre><code>$('#jqGrid').jqGrid("setGridParam", {datatype: "json", url: "grid21.json"});             $("#gs_search").click(function(){                 var text = $("#inputValue").val();                 var postdata = $('#jqGrid').jqGrid('getGridParam','postData');                 $.extend(postdata,{filters:'',searchField: 'lookup_CODE', searchOper: 'cn', stringResult:true, searchString: text});                 $('#jqGrid').jqGrid('setGridParam', { search: text.length&gt;0, postData: postdata });                 $('#jqGrid').trigger("reloadGrid",[{page:1}]);             }); </code></pre>